data.description: Welcome to your dream home nestled in the heart of Clarkdale, where comfort meets convenience. This exquisite property offers the perfect blend of modern living and natural beauty, boasting a prime location near the brand-new community park and other fantastic area attractions.  Beautiful new tile floors on lower level really opens up the space and brightens the room.   Kitchen features a large island for prepping or entertaining, stainless steel appliances, with a separate breakfast nook or office with access to the backyard.  Master bedroom is on the 1st floor.  Beautiful granite counters in the kitchen and bathrooms.  Powder room was recently updated with new toilet and vanity.  This versatile property suits a variety of needs, making it an ideal choice for both owner-occupants and investors. For those looking to establish roots and create cherished memories, this home offers an idyllic setting to raise a family and build a future. On the other hand, savvy investors will appreciate the potential rental income and the growing demand in the area, making it an attractive investment opportunity.  All furnishings, plants etc, are negotiable.
